item.description:
@Travis_02 wrote:

Ykcud:

Your web client has a strange issue where right hand clicking it will bring up both the normal in game options as well as the browser options as well and is far too annoying for someone who uses right hand clicks a lot to play.

There is a add-on from some browsers causing this. It is unknown why I am having this issue. It was fine until recent browser updates in process of fixing.
